er-ps5-features-review&quot;>;&lt;strong>;DualSense Edge&lt;/strong>;&lt;/a >; 售价 174.99 美元（约优惠 24 美元），通过 &lt;a href=&quot;https://goto.walmart.com/c/482924/565706/9383?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FSony- PS5-DualSense-Edge-Wireless-Controller%2F1707140316%2F&amp;amp;sharedid=theverge.com&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;沃尔玛&lt;/a>; 仅限在线交易，将专用游戏手柄降至其迄今为止的最低价格。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;NvCUhY&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component -data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Sony 的 DualSense Edge 是一款（大部分）正确的专业控制器&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23564531/sony-dualsense -edge-wireless-controller-ps5-features-review&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;GuliKit 的防漂移 TMR 摇杆即将适用于您的 PS5、PS4、Xbox 和 Switch Pro 游戏手柄&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/2024/6/13/24177912/gulikit-hall-effect-dualsense-dualshock-4-xbox-series-switch-joystick&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;您现在可以更新 DualSense PS5 PC 上的控制器&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2022/4/20/23033481/sony-dualsense-controller-update-firmware-pc-windows-app-ps5&quot;}]} &#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;2csKh0&quot;>;DualSense Edge 的亮点在于其与 PS5 完美的软件集成。您可以微调最多四个配置文件，每个配置文件都有您自己的个人调整，例如摇杆灵敏度和自定义后按钮控制，并且可以轻松地在配置文件之间进行动态切换。 Edge 还具有标准 DualSense 的所有触觉和功能，以及附加功能，例如一触即发锁定、可互换的顶杆和两个...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge .com/2024/7/9/24194824/sony-dualsense-edge-pro-playstation-controller-ps5-walmart-deal-sale&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/9/24194824/sony-dualsense-edge-pro-playstation-controller-ps5-walmart-deal-sale" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/9/24194824/sony-dualsense-edge-pro-playstation-controller-ps5-walmart-deal-sale</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry></